"{\"uid\": \"thisdaylive.com-2024-03-09-djokovic-targets-olympic-gold-at-41\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  World No 1 Novak Djokovic has not ruled out competing for the Los Angeles Olympic gold in 2028 at the age of 41.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 75, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999731291629395, \"rank\": 2.443643846238489e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-time Grand Slam winner has only managed a bronze in four trips to the Olympics, though he will have another opportunity to improve his medal record in Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995775811823, \"rank\": 4.224190792136621e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic will be 41 by the time the Los Angeles Games roll around but the Serbian says he has not ruled out competing for gold in 2028.\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.356782832979232e-13, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.6106149615527244, \"rank\": 0.6146306950425237, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything is on the cards, I just do not know how many cards I have left,\\\" Djokovic said with a smile when asked about LA 2028.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.356782832979232e-13, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's still very far to think about Los Angeles Olympic Games but the thought of it excites me of course.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 598, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8064665625202689, \"rank\": 0.23997701388856843, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympic Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd love to play that but\\u2026 I can not really commit to that yet.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's becoming harder and harder but I still love this sport and have still been competing at the highest level.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still number one, so I feel at the moment that I want to keep going, keep trying to make more history.\\\"\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic is gunning for a record sixth Indian Wells crown after being unable to enter the US for the past five years due to travel restrictions related to the Covid pandemic.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"score\": 0.9415075170910746, \"rank\": 0.06211928667270677, \"text\": \"Indian Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Wells_Masters\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9196705294776979, \"rank\": 0.08717662255472702, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999990243097939, \"rank\": 9.756910692291706e-07, \"text\": \"Covid pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the tournament three times in a row from 2014-2016 but lost in the third round to now-retired German Philipp Kohlschreiber in his last appearance in 2019.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9777984308851896, \"rank\": 0.020131054248477637, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philipp_Kohlschreiber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philipp Kohlschreiber\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philipp_Kohlschreiber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philipp_Kohlschreiber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is beautiful for our sport that we had amazing rivalries that marked an incredible two decades,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With Roger retiring and Rafa not playing very much at all, it's a strange feeling.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9858700839515617, \"rank\": 0.014332346305602386, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to find a new rival and I had some great matches with (Carlos) Alcaraz and (Jannik) Sinner lately, but they still remain the two biggest rivals I have ever had.\\\"\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.522358288363388e-20, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Founded on January 22, 1995, THISDAY is published by THISDAY NEWSPAPERS LTD., 35 Creek Road Apapa, Lagos, Nigeria with offices in 36 states of Nigeria , the Federal Capital Territory and around the world.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/This_Day\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"THISDAY\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/This_Day\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/This_Day\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_company\", \"score\": 0.9999977745201002, \"rank\": 2.149861203493966e-06, \"text\": \"LTD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_company\"}, {\"begin\": 1770, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lagos\", \"score\": 0.9999900456841485, \"rank\": 9.8720324385